  "payload": {
    "lesson": {
      "language": "zh-CN",
      "title": "椭圆中斜率之积的定值",
      "problem": "<p class='font-medium text-slate-800'>【题目】</p><p>椭圆 $C:\\dfrac{x^2}{4}+\\dfrac{y^2}{3}=1$，$P(2,0)$ 为右顶点。$A,B$ 是 $C$ 上关于原点对称的两点（$B=-A$）。求证 $k_{PA}\\cdot k_{PB}$ 为定值。</p>",
      "answerLabel": "斜率之积定值",
      "answer": "$k_{PA}\\cdot k_{PB}=-\\dfrac{3}{4}$"
    },
    "steps": [
      {
        "title": "设点",
        "content": "<p>设 $A(x_0,y_0)$，则 $B(-x_0,-y_0)$，且 $\\dfrac{x_0^2}{4}+\\dfrac{y_0^2}{3}=1$，即 $y_0^2=3\\left(1-\\dfrac{x_0^2}{4}\\right)=\\dfrac{3(4-x_0^2)}{4}$。</p>"
      },
      {
        "title": "计算斜率之积",
        "content": "<p>$k_{PA}\\cdot k_{PB}=\\dfrac{y_0-0}{x_0-2}\\cdot\\dfrac{-y_0-0}{-x_0-2}=\\dfrac{-y_0^2}{(x_0-2)(-x_0-2)}=\\dfrac{-y_0^2}{4-x_0^2}$。</p><p>代入 $y_0^2=\\dfrac{3(4-x_0^2)}{4}$：</p><div class='text-center py-3 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-xl text-emerald-900 font-bold'>$$ k_{PA}\\cdot k_{PB}=\\dfrac{-\\frac{3}{4}(4-x_0^2)}{4-x_0^2}=-\\dfrac{3}{4} $$</div><p class='text-slate-500 text-sm'>与 $A$ 的位置无关，恒为定值。拖动滑块即可观察。</p>"
      }
    ],
    "board": {
